.page links Alastair Reynolds

Reynolds is an astrophysicist turned writer with a knack for creating trippy,
mind-bending stories.


.section links Revelation Space

_Revelation Space_ is the gateway drug that got me hooked on Reynolds' strange
vision of the future.  It forms a loosely connected trilogy with _Redemption
Ark_ (featuring a riveting near-light-speed chase between the stars spanning
decades) and _Absolution Gap_ (with a virus-induced religious cult, moving
cathedrals and a vanishing gas giant). 

_Aurora Rising_ and _Elysium Fire_ form the
[_Prefect Dreyfuss Emergency_](http://approachingpavonis.blogspot.com/2017/07/elysium-fire-and-new-title-for-prefect.html)
sub-series.  They're police procedurals set in the Glitter Band, a swarm of
thousands of orbital habitats.

